<div class="text"><h2>Message from the Program Director</h2>
<p>&quot;The migration of people, whether forced or voluntary, is one of the most important social, cultural, and economic phenomena of this century. It has dominated politics in Europe and North America, and defines who we are as a nation.</p>
<p>The ISS Program provides fertile ground for knowledge enhancement and in-depth analysis of past and present migration patterns, policies, and practices.&quot;</p>
<h4 style="text-align: right;"><a target="_blank" href="/graduate/programs/immigration/Program_Director_message.html">Read</a>&nbsp;more from the Program Director Dr. Harald Bauder.&nbsp;<br>
